---
layout: base.njk
lang: en
title: "About Us"
description: "Build Hub — Your single point of reference for every project in Sicily. Discover our story, our values and our mission."
root: "../"
permalink: "/en/about.html"
hero_title: "About Us"
hero_subtitle: "Your single point of reference for every project"
storia_title: "How Build Hub was born"
storia_p1: "Build Hub is rooted in direct experience gained on construction sites, in site supervision and in the coordination of technical and operational teams. Over the years we have observed a recurring issue: far too many projects stall not through lack of skill, but through the absence of a guiding figure capable of holding all the pieces together. Professionals, contractors and suppliers often operate in a disconnected way, generating delays, misunderstandings and unexpected costs. It is from this realisation that Build Hub was created: an idea born to bring order to complexity, offering a structured approach to managing construction projects with coordination, planning and oversight at its core. Today we assist private clients, professionals and companies as a single interlocutor, building a bridge between the various parties involved and ensuring a clear, shared and measurable vision of the goals to be achieved."
storia_p2: "We are convinced that every project — regardless of its size or complexity — deserves structured, transparent and results-oriented management. For this reason our involvement does not end with design or the purely technical aspects, but embraces the entire lifecycle of the work: from the preliminary phase through to project handover."
approccio_title: "Our Approach"
approccio_intro: "Our work is based on a structured method, designed to ensure order and clarity at every stage of the project."
approccio_items:
  - "A single interlocutor for the entire project"
  - "Integrated coordination between engineers, contractors and suppliers"
  - "Rigorous control of time, costs and quality"
  - "Clear, transparent and continuous communication"
  - "Constant support through every phase of the project"
visione_title: "Our Vision"
visione_p1: "We aim to contribute to making the construction sector more structured, accessible and efficient, offering clients a working method built on planning, collaboration and control."
visione_p2: "For us, executing a project does not simply mean constructing a building: it means methodically governing every process and every resource required to bring it to completion."
missione_title: "Our Mission"
missione_p1: "We believe that a project's value lies not solely in the quality of its design or execution, but in the ability to effectively coordinate all the people, activities and decisions that constitute it. Build Hub simplifies the management of construction projects through a structured approach, grounded in organisation, planning and continuous oversight."
missione_p2: "Our goal is to enable the client to focus on strategic decisions, confident in the knowledge that they can rely on transparent, measurable and results-oriented management."
valori_title: "Our Values"
valori_cards:
  - title: "Single Interlocutor"
    text: "We are the single interlocutor for private clients, professionals and companies: we build a direct bridge between all the parties involved and ensure a clear, shared and aligned vision of the goals."
  - title: "Coordination & Oversight"
    text: "We oversee time, costs and quality through constant control, orchestrating the work of engineers, contractors and suppliers from the preliminary phase through to project handover."
  - title: "Communication & Support"
    text: "We ensure transparent communication and continuous support through every phase of the project, building a relationship founded on trust and collaboration."
cta_title: "Tell us about your project"
cta_text: "Share your idea: we will support you methodically at every stage of the journey."
cta_button: "Contact Us"
cta_link: "contact.html"
territorio_title: "Rooted in Sicily"
territorio_text: "We operate throughout Sicily with deep-rooted knowledge of local specificities, the regional regulatory framework and the best construction practices of the Mediterranean area."
---

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-glow"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>{{ hero_title }}</h1>
      <p>{{ hero_subtitle }}</p>
      <div class="hero-accent">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 60 12" width="60" height="12">
          <rect x="0" y="5" width="20" height="2" rx="1" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.3"/>
          <rect x="28" y="4" width="4" height="4" rx="1" fill="currentColor"/>
          <rect x="40" y="5" width="20" height="2" rx="1" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.3"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STORY -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="chi-siamo-text reveal">
        <h2>{{ storia_title }}</h2>
        <p>{{ storia_p1 }}</p>
        <p>{{ storia_p2 }}</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- APPROACH -->
  <section class="section bg-surface">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="chi-siamo-text reveal">
        <h2>{{ approccio_title }}</h2>
        <p>{{ approccio_intro }}</p>
        <ul class="servizio-list">
          {% for item in approccio_items %}
          <li><span class="check"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span>{{ item }}</li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VISION + MISSION -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="vision-mission-grid reveal-stagger">
        <div class="vision-box">
          <div class="vm-icon vm-icon--vision">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 2C8.13 2 5 5.13 5 9c0 5.25 7 13 7 13s7-7.75 7-13c0-3.87-3.13-7-7-7z"/><circle cx="12" cy="9" r="2.5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h2>{{ visione_title }}</h2>
          <p>{{ visione_p1 }}</p>
          <p>{{ visione_p2 }}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mission-box">
          <div class="vm-icon vm-icon--mission">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h2>{{ missione_title }}</h2>
          <p>{{ missione_p1 }}</p>
          <p>{{ missione_p2 }}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VALUES -->
  <section class="section bg-surface">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">{{ valori_title }}</h2>
      <div class="valori-grid reveal-stagger">
        {% for card in valori_cards %}
        <div class="card">
          {% if loop.first %}
          <div class="card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg></div>
          {% elif loop.index == 2 %}
          <div class="card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"/><path d="M12 1v2M12 21v2M4.22 4.22l1.42 1.42M18.36 18.36l1.42 1.42M1 12h2M21 12h2M4.22 19.78l1.42-1.42M18.36 5.64l1.42-1.42"/></svg></div>
          {% else %}
          <div class="card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C8.13 2 5 5.13 5 9c0 5.25 7 13 7 13s7-7.75 7-13c0-3.87-3.13-7-7-7z"/><circle cx="12" cy="9" r="2.5"/></svg></div>
          {% endif %}
          <h3>{{ card.title }}</h3>
          <p>{{ card.text }}</p>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <div class="reveal" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">{{ cta_title }}</h2>
        <p style="color: rgba(10,10,10,0.6); font-size: 1.125rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">{{ cta_text }}</p>
        <a href="{{ cta_link }}" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
          {{ cta_button }}
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TERRITORY -->
  <section class="territorio-section">
    <div class="territorio-glow"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="reveal">
        <div class="territorio-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M82.3 79.5L81.5 73.5L84.4 69.1L88.2 67.2L86.5 66.3L87.1 63.9L85.3 63.3L83.7 60.4L83.9 59.0L85.9 58.6L84.4 56.9L81.3 56.0L80.9 49.9L83.6 46.2L84.6 39.7L92.9 27.8L95.4 21.4L97.5 20.4L93.8 19.4L87.3 22.8L85.8 22.7L85.2 20.4L84.8 23.3L81.8 25.7L75.8 23.4L70.8 24.5L66.3 28.3L57.7 30.3L49.6 29.0L41.3 31.6L36.1 29.1L35.3 26.4L30.8 26.5L28.8 22.2L25.1 24.2L22.1 23.8L21.0 25.4L21.4 27.6L16.8 29.6L14.4 28.1L11.6 23.6L11.1 26.3L4.6 30.0L5.7 30.6L4.6 31.2L3.5 34.0L4.3 35.4L2.5 37.9L4.0 41.8L8.1 44.1L9.5 46.7L17.1 46.3L20.3 49.3L24.5 49.6L32.1 56.4L35.8 57.1L38.9 60.3L45.2 63.9L51.5 63.7L56.5 65.5L60.3 69.4L63.5 75.5L71.9 78.6L74.4 77.6L78.8 78.6L80.8 80.6L82.3 79.5Z"/></svg></div>
        <h2>{{ territorio_title }}</h2>
        <p>{{ territorio_text }}</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
